Package: objectSetsR
Type: Package
Title: Lazy Ontology-Aware Object Sets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("ObjectSetsR", "Maintainer", email = "maintainer@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides a lazy, ontology-aware query algebra for object types and
  link traversals defined in ontologySpecR bundles. Object sets can be filtered,
  traversed, aggregated, and materialized against DBI backends such as DuckDB.
